import Gluck.Winding

/-!
# Spherical compatibility re-export for the conjugate-loop winding

The conjugate loop used by the spherical endpoint argument is the reverse
exponential loop `Gluck.expLoopRev`; the public compatibility names
`conjLoop`, `conjLoop_ne_zero`, and `windingNumberC_conj_loop` now live in
`Gluck.Winding`.
-/
